OL,5, The average cost of a basic funeral has
OL,6, dropped for the first time in 18 years,
OL,7, but is predicted to rise again in the  
OL,8, future, a report has found.            
OL,10,FFuneral costs fell 3.1% to an average  
OL,11,Fof #4,056 last year, the Cost of Dying 
OL,12,Freport by insurer SunLife found.       
OL,14,FCosts are varied across the UK, and the
OL,15,Fcheapest type of ceremony - a cremation
OL,16,Fwithout a service - rose in price.     
OL,18,FLast year, funeral firms were ordered  
OL,19,Fto display clearer price lists for     
OL,20,Fbereaved customers.                    
